The largest amount of candidate reactions are:
Valine, Leucine, and Isoleucine metabolic pathway: 7 reactions (25, 93%);
Threonine and Lysine pathway: 6 reactions (22, 22%)
Tyrosine, Tryptophan and Phenylalanine pathway: 5 reactions (18, 52%);
